{"tid":1616731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［麗晶3.0］國殤日葵涌邨保安助狗拉左14 個街坊 比居民圍屌中","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T18:12:28.000Z","uid":282490,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d3032ad78053e34fb71b1a28a02b65ed92e4fe75","tid":1616731,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"事情經過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNd6npm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNd6npm.png&h=059ca48f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n街坊證言：<br />\n街坊話1.10 四點幾已經有狗入商場廁所逐格搜<br />\n<br />\n保安搵水馬擋住出入口 係咪幫警察圍捕<br />\n保安公司回應話撤水馬係為左比返條路居民行<br />\n<br />\n街坊話1.10 比3 隻狗圍 <br />\n<br />\n葵涌邨保安喺無搜查令情況下比警察入保安室睇cctv<br />\n職員交左cctv 比狗<br />\n房署代表話有搜查令，街坊即屌話搜查令申請至少要一日<br />\n<br />\n夜更保安鎖商場大門比狗捉人<br />\n綠狗12 點反Cup 果陣捉左三個剛落街嘅女街坊<br />\n<br />\n狗半夜上左樓搜索 但保安無登記狗名<br />\n<br />\n街坊話仲見到涉事助狗圍捕街坊嘅保安仲返緊工<br />\n希望保安公司炒人解除街坊憂慮<br />\n保安公司話唔可以無理解僱<br />\n<br />\n保安公司代表話佢真係當日唔在場 你地咁激動都無用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n房署回應：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m2rLCX1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm2rLCX1.png&h=956283bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在居民大會，房署代表同保安公司被街坊圍屌中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyKdMTz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyKdMTz.jpg&h=0a4d0f29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXCffM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXCffM5.png&h=2f4eaced&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgCZHsh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgCZHsh.png&h=7b06a9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PERch0N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPERch0N.png&h=66ea35c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad9608bf1a5fbff1c522f8cd42f1ea659f361da8","tid":1616731,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=38424108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"d910d74d58fd0cdc7fe2b67a704135fc97494549","tid":1616731,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"唔記得講 <br />\n最尾幾張相係當日情況"},{"pid":"70c6bf819a8f438564217590f6414ac39d14ecb9","tid":1616731,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"保安公司：商場係公眾範圍，一定要廿四小時開放...<br />\n街坊：咁入大廈呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4b6c4af1ac89f8110ebfc138fce20e26ab9202","tid":1616731,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:57:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8967388f6420c33b11054427c1ce8939062d882d","tid":1616731,"uid":282490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"當日情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJVDX5j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJVDX5j.jpg&h=1eb6ae2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uEHw0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uEHw0.jpg&h=a2011e39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"701c49dcd4414bfc40843c11cb3e168648ac67a9","tid":1616731,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:07:47.000Z